title: Roger Stone - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 5/9/18

description:
George Noory and famed political strategist Roger Stone discuss his work assisting the presidential campaign of Donald Trump, and the ongoing efforts to disrupt the presidency with allegations of Russian collusion in the 2016 election.
